      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear u on the individual stuff, but i'm just trying to be realistic for my business. if i'm looking at a group and i don't want to waste time, wouldn't it be more efficient to use those \"trends\" you mentioned to guide how i set up the drills? like, if there are actual statistical tendencies in certain populations for things like explosive power vs endurance, shouldn't a professional sports scientist be able to tell me what those are so i can plan better? i'm not trying to be biased, i just want to know what the data actually says about these trends.",
